title: I got Kayle skin but not the summoner icon

embed.description: When we started this journey 10 years ago, we had no idea what Riot and League would become. Luckily, we were carried forward by the passion of a player community that continues to grow and evolve, ten years later. There's nothing more to say beyond thank you.

body:
It says that you get the summoner icon along with the kayle skin, but i only got the kayle skin.
Is there something im missing? I know that i've played a game in the last few months so that shouldn't be the problem.

replies.body: It's going to take a bit for everything to roll out to every eligible account, so you may not get everything all at once.  We have updated our [support ticker ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-)as gifts continue to be sent out.  Hang tight!
Alright, ill let you know when ive got it.
